elements.name: Verify Applying for the Sales Specialist Position

steps.name: I hover over the "Company" section in the menu bar
I click on the "Careers" button from dropdown
I see that the page URL should be contain the "/company/careers"
I see that the page URL should be contain the "/company/careers/sales_specialist"
I fill in "fullName_" field with "nameTest" value
I fill in "email_" field with "test@test.com" value
I fill in "phone_" field with "12345678910" value
I check the I agree to checkbox from Careers
I should see the succses message "Success"
